## Transition Criteria

{% if phaseOrder == "1" %}
Before proceeding to Measure, participants should demonstrate:
- Approved project charter with clearly defined problem and scope
- Documented MGPP with measurable goals and timeline
- Completed stakeholder analysis and communication plan
{% elif phaseOrder == "2" %}
Before proceeding to Explore, participants should demonstrate:
- Validated measurement system (MSA Gage R&R < 30%)
- Baseline process capability (Cpk documented)
- Completed QFD with customer requirements mapped to technical specs
{% elif phaseOrder == "3" %}
Before proceeding to Develop, participants should demonstrate:
- Completed concept selection (Pugh matrix or AHP) with rationale
- Statistical analysis supporting design decisions
- Design FMEA with RPN prioritization of failure modes
{% elif phaseOrder == "4" %}
Before proceeding to Implement, participants should demonstrate:
- Validated DOE results with confirmation runs
- Optimized design parameters from RSM
- Reliability prediction meeting targets
{% elif phaseOrder == "5" %}
Before final certification, participants should demonstrate:
- Successful prototype/pilot with measured improvements
- Statistical process control charts established
- Comprehensive capstone report with business impact quantified
{% endif %}

## Quality Checkpoints

{% if phaseOrder == "1" %}
- [ ] Project charter approved by sponsor
- [ ] MGPP (Multigeneration Plan) documented
- [ ] Risk management plan established
- [ ] Team roles and communication plan defined
- [ ] CTQ flowdowns completed
{% elif phaseOrder == "2" %}
- [ ] Voice of Customer captured and analyzed
- [ ] QFD (House of Quality) completed
- [ ] Metrics and scorecards established
- [ ] Measurement system analysis validated
- [ ] Process capability assessed
{% elif phaseOrder == "3" %}
- [ ] Concept generation using TRIZ completed
- [ ] Pugh concept selection documented
- [ ] Tolerance analysis performed
- [ ] Monte Carlo simulation completed
- [ ] Hypothesis testing validated
{% elif phaseOrder == "4" %}
- [ ] ANOVA results documented
- [ ] DOE (full-factorial and fractional) completed
- [ ] RSM model validated
- [ ] Reliability targets verified
- [ ] Robust design parameters optimized
{% elif phaseOrder == "5" %}
- [ ] Prototype testing completed
- [ ] Pilot results validated
- [ ] SPC charts established
- [ ] Implementation plan approved
- [ ] Capstone project presented
{% endif %}

## Prerequisites

{% if phaseOrder == "1" %}
No prerequisites — this is the first phase.
{% else %}
Completion of the preceding DMEDI phase is required.
{% endif %}

